     C*
     C                     Z-ADD*ZERO     WCNT    30
TCHK3C*                    ADD  Q5N1NM    W5N1NM
     C                     ADD  Q5NNNM    W5NNNM
     C                     ADD  Q51NNM    W51NNM
TCHK3C                     ADD  Q52NNM    W52NNM
     C           KEY1      SETLLMCENP131
     C           KEY1      READEMCENP131                 93
B01  C           *IN93     DOWEQ'0'
